--   ⊨ proof-sketch contains at least 4 logical steps → ✓
--     (5 propositions: invariant, termination, found, not-found, empty-array)
--   ⊨ invariants includes a loop invariant referencing lo, hi, and target → ✓
--     ("target is in arr[lo..hi]" — references all three)
--   ⊨ termination-argument identifies a decreasing quantity bounded below → ✓
--     ("V = hi - lo + 1", "decreases by at least 1", "bounded below by 0")
